$ cd redmine
</code></pre>

<ul>
<li>remove those files from .gitignore
<code>
Gemfile.lock
Gemfile.local
public/plugin_assets
config/initializers/session_store.rb
config/initializers/secret_token.rb
config/configuration.yml
config/email.yml
</code></li>
</ul>


